snippet.textDisplay: After the three kingdoms，the western Jin dynasty united China. There wasn't many years when the eight kings abrupted a war about the inheritance of emporer. At that time，the northern minorities attacked the captaial Luo Yang，which ended the empire. Meanwhile，the king of langya established the eastern Jin in southen China. And in the north of China，the northern Wei was established by xianbei nationality. And the famous Mu Lan was from the northern Wei dynasty. Actually，the northern Wei was the enermy of China at that time.But with the development of China，xianbei was gone and become the part of Han nationality. The previous enermy become the present hero. The history history is funny，isn't it?
